The paper proposes a novel convolution block for video and volumetric data understanding, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions applications such as MRI brain segmentation and electron microscopy segmentation, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Lastly, the paper discusses the improvement in test performance, which suggests a potential application in neural networks (cs.NE).
